chunk_id: Membership Updates_5732730f
source_id: Membership Updates
title: Membership Updates
headers: Meet the New Note Ninja AI Bot: Note Ninja Wiz

We’ve spent months training this tool using years of Note Ninjas content—so it doesn’t just give you generic advice. It gives you our strategies, documentation examples, and treatment ideas, instantly.
Whether you're looking for a creative balance activity, skilled documentation language, or a quick way to write goals—Note Ninja Wiz is here to help you work smarter, not harder.
Try it out and see how fast and easy treatment planning and documentation can be.

Supporting a Loved One with Sundowning: Caregiver Tips

What is Sundowning? Sundowning is when individuals with dementia become more confused or agitated later in the day. It often starts in the late afternoon and can lead to restlessness, mood changes, or wandering.
